id: cooking-root
name: Cooking
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: >
  A cabinet for cooking at home — what's in the fridge, what's about to expire,
  what to make tonight. Recipe Tonight webapp picks dinner from your pantry,
  weekly meal plan generates the shopping list, recipes are saved with notes
  so the next time you make them they're better. One agent: Chef.
entry: index.md
